Property.Name: 72-h Algal toxicity as log(1/EC50)
Property.Description: Measured by the OECD 201 test protocol, collected from the FOOTPRINT Pesticide Properties Database (PPDB) with higher quality-scores: 4 (verified data) and 5 (verified data used for regulatory purposes) and 13 (B)TAZs tested within CADASTER project. The experimental range was from 3.09 to 6.72 log units.
Property.Endpoint: 3. Ecotoxic effects 3.2. Short-term toxicity to algae
